  "local_port": 58430,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What I have to do If I didn't get mail for location selection from congnizant or cognizant pre joining formalities mail?",
  "response": "If you haven't received the mail for location selection or pre-joining formalities from Cognizant, here\u2019s what you can do:\n\n---\n\n### **1. Check Your Spam/Junk Folder**\nSometimes, emails from companies land in the spam or junk folder. Check these folders in your email account to ensure the mail hasn\u2019t been filtered there.\n\n---\n\n### **2. Verify Your Registered Email Address**\nEnsure that Cognizant has the correct email address on file. If you\u2019ve changed your email address or there\u2019s a typo, you may not receive the mail.\n\n---\n\n### **3. Contact Cognizant HR or Recruitment Team**\nIf you still haven\u2019t received the mail, reach out to the Cognizant HR or recruitment team. Here\u2019s how:\n   - **Look for contact details** in previous communication from Cognizant (e.g., offer letter, interview emails).\n   - Use the **Cognizant careers portal** or official website to find the relevant contact information.\n   - Send a polite email explaining the situation and requesting guidance on the next steps.\n\n---\n\n### **4. Check the Portals**\nLog in to the **Cognizant careers portal** or any pre-joining portal provided to you. Sometimes, updates or instructions are posted there instead of being sent via email.\n\n---\n\n### **5. Stay Proactive**\nDon\u2019t wait too long to follow up. Delays in pre-joining formalities could affect your onboarding process.\n\n---\n\n**Sample Email Template to Reach Out:**\n\nSubject: Follow-Up on Location Selection/Pre-Joining Formalities  \n\nDear [HR/Recruitment Team],  \n\nI hope this email finds you well. I am writing to inquire about the next steps in the onboarding process, as I have not yet received the mail regarding location selection or pre-joining formalities.  \n\nCould you please guide me on how to proceed or confirm if there\u2019s any additional information required from my end? I want to ensure everything is completed smoothly and on time.  \n\nThank you for your assistance. Looking forward to your response.  \n\nBest regards,  \n[Your Full Name]  \n[Your Contact Information]  \n[Employee ID or Reference Number, if applicable]  \n\n---\n\nBy taking these steps, you can ensure that you stay on track with the onboarding process.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
